{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-changelog-js","path":"/changelog/2019/october","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3 id=\"hacker-profile-redesign\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hacker-profile-redesign\" aria-label=\"hacker profile redesign permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Hacker Profile Redesign</h3>\n<p>We've redesigned the hacker profile page to simplify the UI. In doing so, we've deprecated the <strong>Thanks</strong> tab and put the <strong>Thanks</strong> section at the bottom of the profile page.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.80000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"profile page\"\n        title=\"profile page\"\n        src=\"/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/0b533/oct_2019_profile_page.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/fac75/oct_2019_profile_page.png 125w,\n/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/63868/oct_2019_profile_page.png 250w,\n/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/0b533/oct_2019_profile_page.png 500w,\n/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/1d69c/oct_2019_profile_page.png 750w,\n/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/00d43/oct_2019_profile_page.png 1000w,\n/static/aeb5edb48ffd890f626d72aca0f7add8/5f652/oct_2019_profile_page.png 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"new-settings-on-notification-preferences\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#new-settings-on-notification-preferences\" aria-label=\"new settings on notification preferences permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>New Settings on Notification Preferences</h3>\n<p>We've revamped the Notification Preferences page and added new settings so that all users can better customize their report notifications to reduce noise from unwanted notifications.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 79.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"notification preferences\"\n        title=\"notification preferences\"\n        src=\"/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/0b533/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/fac75/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png 125w,\n/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/63868/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png 250w,\n/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/0b533/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png 500w,\n/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/1d69c/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png 750w,\n/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/00d43/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png 1000w,\n/static/67289d8a3c58bede391e6b3f514bf799/8b640/oct_2019_notification_preferences.png 1454w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"program-page-bookmark-and-subscribe-buttons\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#program-page-bookmark-and-subscribe-buttons\" aria-label=\"program page bookmark and subscribe buttons permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Program Page Bookmark and Subscribe Buttons</h3>\n<p>We've deprecated the <strong>Follow</strong> button on the Program Page and replaced it with a <strong>Bookmark</strong> button. We also moved the <strong>Subscribe</strong> button from the bottom of the Program Page and moved it to the top next to the new <strong>Bookmark</strong> button so that hackers can easily subscribe to program updates and add programs to their bookmarked program list on their dashboard.   </p>\n<p> <span\n  