ansactions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#programs-get-balance\">Getting a program's balance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#programs-get-thanks-to-hackers\">Fetching a program's thanks items</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#reports-update-structured-scope\">Updating report structured scope</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#reports-get-all-reports\">Filtering reports by keywords</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#programs-get-awarded-swag\">Fetching awarded program swag</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#reports-get-bounty-suggestions\">Fetching bounty suggestions</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#programs-get-program\">Fetching program policy and attachments</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#core-resources-reports-manage-disclosure-request\">Requesting and cancelling report disclosure</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#core-resources-reports-redact\">Redacting reports</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/#core-resources-programs-get-program\">Groups attribute to member object</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://api.hackerone.com/core-resources/#programs-upload-policy-attachment\">Uploading attachments to the policy page</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/changelog/2019/october","title":"October 2019"}}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}